abstract: Shootout in Phoenix park leaves young Arizona men Miguel Lopez Retana, Alberto Garcia and Oscar Garcia Armenta dead.
lead_paragraph: An exchange of gunfire between groups of people in a Phoenix park left three men dead.

headline.main: Arizona: Three Men Are Killed in Shooting at a Phoenix Park
